// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dtjcDW hexagonal rocks - triangular sea by jt
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dlByWW Hexagonally Grouped Triangle DDA
// and https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DtfXzS Triangle Terrain (via Voxel DDA)
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mlfXD7 Triangle DDA via Voxel DDA Slice
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mtfXDM Branchless Voxel Raycasting Tex2
// clean-up of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/7dK3D3 Branchless Voxel Raycasting Tex
// using voxel DDA of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/4dX3zl Branchless Voxel Raycasting by fb39ca4
// (with loop optimization by kzy), DDA based on http://lodev.org/cgtutor/raycasting.html

// Playing around with a structure resembling basalt columns in polygonal water.

